Selected Answer: A
Tested it today in Utah, as well as in San Diego. Both times UI Policy Action got executed before UI Policy Script. So A must be correct

see my test:
UI Policy Action: Make field mandatory (which is not mandatory by default)
UI Policy Script:
function onCondition() {
 if(g_form.isMandatory("business_service"))
 g_form.addInfoMessage("Is mandatory");
 else g_form.addInfoMessage("Was not mandatory");
}

got result: "Is mandatory", so UI Action did proceed before UI Policy Script

